## Summary
Notivize is a no-code platform for product engagement notifications that integrates with Amplitude for cohort syncing. The documentation details the setup process requiring an API key from Notivize's settings and configuring the destination in Amplitude Data, followed by steps to export cohorts with customizable sync cadence.

